==English==

===Noun===
'''chromatophore'''  (''plural:'' '''[[chromatophores]]''')

# A [[pigment]] bearing [[cell]] or structure found in animals such as fish, reptiles and cephalophods.
#:''Cuttlefish skin contains chromatophores which enable it to change color.''

